im-Dyson-min.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="新秩序、尼克·凯夫和垃圾。致谢——Harmony Gerber、吉姆·戴森" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/New-Order-Nick-Cave-and-Garbage.-Credits-Harmony-Gerber-Jim-Dyson-min.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/New-Order-Nick-Cave-and-Garbage.-Credits-Harmony-Gerber-Jim-Dyson-min-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/New-Order-Nick-Cave-and-Garbage.-Credits-Harmony-Gerber-Jim-Dyson-min-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/New-Order-Nick-Cave-and-Garbage.-Credits-Harmony-Gerber-Jim-Dyson-min-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/New-Order-Nick-Cave-and-Garbage.-Credits-Harmony-Gerber-Jim-Dyson-min-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/New-Order-Nick-Cave-and-Garbage.-Credits-Harmony-Gerber-Jim-Dyson-min-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/new-order">New Order</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nick-cave-and-the-bad-seeds">Nick Cave、The Bad Seeds</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/garbage">Garbage</a>是 2025 年残酷世界音乐节阵容中的领军人物。</p><p>明年的赛事定于 5 月 17 日在加利福尼亚州帕萨迪纳的布鲁克赛德玫瑰碗体育场拉开帷幕。阵容中还包括 The <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/go-gos">Go-Gos</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/devo">Devo</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/madness">Madness</a> 、Orchestral Maneuvers in the Dark、&#39;Til Tuesday、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/alison-moyet">Alison Moyet</a> 、Death Cult、Mareux、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/she-wants-revenge">She Wants Revenge</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chelsea-wolfe">Chelsea Wolfe。</a></p><p> Cruel World Festival 的门票将于太平洋时间 10 月 25 日星期五上午 11 点开始发售，但粉丝们可以立即<a href="https://cruelworldfest.com/#register">注册</a>以抢先体验。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.i